17:04.957 --> 17:07.653
PlERCE: It's going down.
Pierce is going to be the only person

17:07.859 --> 17:10.954
ever to drown in a parking lot,
twice.

17:11.163 --> 17:12.425
[LAUGHlNG]

17:14.133 --> 17:16.032
Help!
Damn the storm.

17:16.234 --> 17:17.395
We're going after Pierce.

17:17.603 --> 17:20.867
Jump the halyard.
Star-Burns, get down there
and man the iron jinny.

17:21.073 --> 17:23.666
There's a man overboard.
That's an order.

17:23.876 --> 17:25.207
PlERCE:
I'm gonna sink.

17:25.676 --> 17:27.974
I'm about to get the only A
I will ever get,

17:28.180 --> 17:30.842
and Pierce isn't even dying.
Bailing.

17:31.050 --> 17:32.517
You don't have to do this.

17:32.718 --> 17:33.707
I know.

17:33.919 --> 17:37.411
But I'd rather be kind
and get stepped on
every once in a while

17:37.623 --> 17:40.558
than be a hard-ass
and turn my back on a friend.

17:40.759 --> 17:42.021
Hoist the mains.

17:44.396 --> 17:45.385
[CRYlNG]

17:45.597 --> 17:48.065
I don't want to go this way.

17:49.268 --> 17:51.236
[§§§]

17:51.703 --> 17:53.864
SHlRLEY:
We're coming, Pierce.

17:54.073 --> 17:55.768
PlERCE:
Help.

17:55.974 --> 17:58.670
SHlRLEY: How's it looking?
BRlTTA: We've gotta go faster.

17:58.877 --> 18:00.401
Okay, come on, Star-Burns.

18:00.612 --> 18:02.102
BRlTTA:
It's filling with water.

18:12.424 --> 18:13.618
It's going down.

18:13.826 --> 18:15.885
Pierce, we're coming.

18:16.095 --> 18:18.563
Dear God. Dear God.

18:23.936 --> 18:25.733
Oh, yes. Oh, Britta.

18:25.938 --> 18:27.064
Troy.

18:29.842 --> 18:31.776
Here you go. We gotcha.

18:31.977 --> 18:33.239
Here you go.
Okay.

18:33.912 --> 18:35.243
[LAUGHS]

18:35.881 --> 18:37.610
SHlRLEY: Are you okay?
You all right?

18:37.816 --> 18:41.081
You just steered
your boat into a storm.
Any last words?

18:41.286 --> 18:45.689
The sea may be cold
and unforgiving,
but I'm not.

18:46.692 --> 18:50.958
The ship might go down
but at least she'll go down
with honor.

18:51.163 --> 18:52.824
Then I'll take
your captain's hat

18:53.031 --> 18:54.828
because I'm promoting
you to admiral.

18:55.033 --> 18:56.432
You all get an A.
Oh.

18:56.635 --> 18:58.296
Admiral Shirley. I like that.

18:58.504 --> 19:01.769
Well, it means nothing,
really, the class is over.
But you deserve it.

19:01.974 --> 19:03.965
Hey, somebody has to do this.

19:04.176 --> 19:05.165
I'm king of the--

19:05.377 --> 19:07.345
[WHlSTLE BLOWlNG]

19:08.080 --> 19:09.604
Don't ruin a perfect week.

19:09.815 --> 19:11.783
[§§§]

19:12.818 --> 19:16.379
I'm not gonna spoon you again.
I appreciate that.

19:16.588 --> 19:19.079
Yeah, I can't fully explain
my behavior.

19:19.291 --> 19:21.555
I'd love to blame booze
or demon possession--

19:21.760 --> 19:24.661
You know what?
Don't worry about it.
I'm bad at holding grudges.

19:24.863 --> 19:26.194
Well, I'm bad at pottery.

19:26.398 --> 19:29.196
I'm an amateur pottery enthusiast

19:29.401 --> 19:33.565
