at something I suck at.
It's great.

19:33.772 --> 19:37.902
And the teacher said
I could stay if I don't have
any more Ghost bursts.

19:38.110 --> 19:40.374
Fantastic. Well, good luck.

19:41.246 --> 19:42.804
Don't need it.

19:44.883 --> 19:47.647
JEFF'S MOM:
Jeff, you're a normal person.

19:47.853 --> 19:50.151
There's nothing very special
about you at all.

19:50.355 --> 19:53.017
You're going to be great
at a few things

19:53.225 --> 19:55.250
but really crappy
at many more.

19:55.460 --> 19:57.587
And that takes a lot
of the pressure off

19:57.796 --> 20:00.390
so you can live
a full, happy life.

20:01.366 --> 20:04.563
Oh, and sorry it took me so long
to tell you that

20:04.770 --> 20:06.829
